      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes more sense. thanks. so once the concrete is poured and hardens, how do they actually stay bonded together? like, is it just friction or is there a chemical thing happening there to make sure the steel doesn't just slide out of the concrete when it's under load?",
      "source": "evaluator"
